Class AddProductMenuController

java.lang.Object
controller.AddProductMenuController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AddProductMenuController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The AddProductMenuController Class. Provides control logic to the AddProductMenu to allow new products to be added using user input from text fields and the ability to add associated parts to the product.
